            "policy_content": "<p><strong>Website:</strong> sundaze.com<br/><strong>Contact:</strong> support@sundaze.com</p><p>Sundaze ships hemp-derived products only where permitted by applicable law and carrier rules.</p><h2>1. Age Requirement</h2><p>You must be 21 years of age or older to place an order.</p><p>By purchasing from Sundaze, you confirm that:</p><ul><li>You are 21 years of age or older.</li><li>You are legally allowed to receive hemp-derived products at your shipping address.</li></ul><p>We reserve the right to require age verification before processing or delivering an order.</p><h2>2. Shipping Locations</h2><p>Sundaze currently ships only within the United States where permitted by law.</p><p>We do not ship internationally.</p><p>We do not ship to any state, city, county, territory, military address, P.O. Box, or jurisdiction where hemp-derived THCA products, smokable hemp, infused hemp products, or related products are prohibited or restricted.</p><h2>3. Restricted States and Locations</h2><p>Sundaze reserves the right to block, cancel, or refuse orders shipping to restricted jurisdictions.</p><p>We do not ship to any jurisdiction where hemp-derived THCA, smokable hemp, infused hemp products, or related products are prohibited or restricted. Our restricted shipping list may change at any time based on federal, state, local, carrier, payment-processor, or banking requirements.</p><h2>4. Processing Times</h2><p>Orders are typically processed within <strong>1–3 business days</strong>, excluding weekends and holidays.</p><p>Processing times may be longer during high-volume periods, product launches, holidays, compliance reviews, or carrier delays.</p><h2>5. Delivery Times</h2><p>Estimated delivery times vary by carrier and destination.</p><p>Delivery estimates are not guaranteed.</p><p>Sundaze is not responsible for carrier delays, weather delays, misrouted packages, failed delivery attempts, or other events outside our control.</p><h2>6. Shipping Confirmation and Tracking</h2><p>Once your order ships, you may receive a tracking number by email or SMS.</p><p>Tracking updates are controlled by the carrier and may take time to appear.</p><h2>7. Address Accuracy</h2><p>Customers are responsible for entering accurate shipping information.</p><p>Please double-check your:</p><ul><li>Full name</li><li>Street address</li><li>Apartment or unit number</li><li>City</li><li>State</li><li>ZIP code</li><li>Phone number</li><li>Email address</li></ul><p>Sundaze is not responsible for orders delayed, lost, returned, or delivered incorrectly due to customer address errors.</p><h2>8. Carrier Restrictions</h2><p>Some carriers may restrict hemp-derived products or require specific shipping procedures.</p><p>Sundaze reserves the right to choose, change, or limit shipping carriers based on compliance, availability, cost, product type, or destination.</p><h2>9. Returned Packages</h2><p>If a package is returned to Sundaze due to failed delivery, incorrect address, refusal, restricted location, or customer error, the order is not automatically eligible for a refund.</p><p>Sundaze may, in its sole discretion, offer:</p><ul><li>Reshipment at the customer's expense</li><li>Store credit</li><li>Replacement</li><li>No remedy</li></ul><p>depending on the circumstances.</p><h2>10. Lost, Stolen, or Delivered Packages</h2><p>Sundaze is not responsible for packages marked as delivered by the carrier.</p><p>If your package is lost in transit or marked delivered but not received:</p><ol><li>Contact the carrier first.</li><li>Contact us at <strong>support@sundaze.com</strong>.</li></ol><h2>11. Compliance Cancellations</h2><p>Sundaze may cancel any order if we determine that shipping the product may violate applicable law, carrier policy, payment-processor policy, or internal compliance standards.</p><h2>12. Contact</h2><p>For shipping questions, contact:</p><p><strong>Sundaze Support</strong><br/><strong>Email:</strong> support@sundaze.com</p>"
